", "bbox": [1081.2, 1159.9, 1102.1, 1180.7]}, {"text": "Expected long-term rate of return on plan assets . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [162.5, 1182.8, 706.2, 1203.7]}, {"text": "7.19% 6.80% 7.37%", "bbox": [737.5, 1182.6, 926.7, 1203.7]}, {"text": "—", "bbox": [945.8, 1182.6, 966.7, 1203.4]}, {"text": "—", "bbox": [1013.5, 1182.8, 1034.4, 1203.7]}, {"text": "—", "bbox": [1081.2, 1182.8, 1102.1, 1203.7]}, {"text": "The Company’s pension and postretirement benefit costs are developed from actuarial valuations. These", "bbox": [204.2, 1233.2, 1075.4, 1254.1]}, {"text": "valuations reflect key assumptions provided by the Company to our actuaries, including the discount rate and", "bbox": [162.5, 1258.2, 1074.9, 1279.1]}, {"text": "expected long-term rate of return on plan assets. Material changes in the Company’s pension and postretirement", "bbox": [162.5, 1283.2, 1097.9, 1304.1]}, {"text": "benefit costs may occur in the future due to changes in these assumptions.", "bbox": [162.5, 1308.2, 779.7, 1329.1]}, {"text": "The discount rate is subject to change each year, consistent with changes in applicable high-quality, long-", "bbox": [204.2, 1358.7, 1085.8, 1379.5]}, {"text": "term corporate bond indices. Based on the expected duration of the benefit payments for our pension plans and", "bbox": [162.5, 1383.7, 1087.5, 1404.5]}, {"text": "postretirement plans, we refer to an applicable index and expected cash flows to select a rate at which we believe", "bbox": [162.5, 1408.7, 1106.0, 1429.5]}, {"text": "the pension benefits could be effectively settled.", "bbox": [162.5, 1433.7, 565.3, 1454.5]}, {"text": "69", "bbox": [627.1, 1484.1, 647.9, 1504.9]}]}